      ingredients:"1 1/2 cups lard or vegetable shortening, at room temperature, 4 cups masa harina, 1 teaspoon baking powder, 1/2 tablespoon salt, 3 3/4 cups warm chicken stock or water, divided (see Recipe Note)",
